ge-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt66\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> Notionally at the speaker's location by virtue of happening now.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Flu season is <b>here</b>."},{"example":"Christmas will soon be <b>here</b>."}],"examples":["Flu season is <b>here</b>.","Christmas will soon be <b>here</b>."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt69\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> In this <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/context\" title=\"context\">context</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Derivatives can refer to anything that is derived from something else, but <b>here</b> they refer specifically to functions that give the slope of the tangent line to a curve."}],"examples":["Derivatives can refer to anything that is derived from something else, but <b>here</b> they refer specifically to functions that give the slope of the tangent line to a curve."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt73\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt74\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">After the name of a person perceived as located close to the speaker, used familiarly to indicate that person.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Jim <b>here</b> has been with the company for twenty years."}],"examples":["Jim <b>here</b> has been with the company for twenty years."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt76\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt77\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">After certain determiners, especially 'this' and 'these', used to emphasise demonstrative sense<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> see also <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/this_here#English\" title=\"this here\">this here</a></b>.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"This <b>here</b> orange is too sour."},{"example":"Both <b><span>'</span>ere</b> buckets 'ave 'oles in 'em."}],"examples":["This <b>here</b> orange is too sour.","Both <b><span>'</span>ere</b> buckets 'ave 'oles in 'em."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt80\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> To this <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/place\" title=\"place\">place</a>; <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt81\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">used in place of the literary or archaic <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/hither#English\" title=\"hither\">hither</a></span>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Please come <b>here</b>."}],"examples":["Please come <b>here</b>."]}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Adjective","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/alive\" title=\"alive\">Alive</a>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"I'm not dead yet<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>  I'm still <b>here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>"}],"examples":["I'm not dead yet<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>  I'm still <b>here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>"]}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"This <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/place\" title=\"place\">place</a>; this <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/location\" title=\"location\">location</a>.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"<b>Here</b> is where I met my spouse twelve years ago."},{"example":"An Alzheimer patient's <b>here</b> may in his mind be anywhere he called home in the time he presently re-lives."},{"example":"I'd like to continue my story, but <b>here</b> is where I must stop."},{"example":"I've done as much as I can<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> you'll have to take it from <b>here</b>."}],"examples":["<b>Here</b> is where I met my spouse twelve years ago.","An Alzheimer patient's <b>here</b> may in his mind be anywhere he called home in the time he presently re-lives.","I'd like to continue my story, but <b>here</b> is where I must stop.","I've done as much as I can<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> you'll have to take it from <b>here</b>."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt100\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> This <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/point\" title=\"point\">point</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/stage\" title=\"stage\">stage</a> in time, conceptualised as a location.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"I'd like to continue my story, but <b>here</b> is where I must stop."},{"example":"I've done as much as I can<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> you'll have to take it from <b>here</b>."}],"examples":["I'd like to continue my story, but <b>here</b> is where I must stop.","I've done as much as I can<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> you'll have to take it from <b>here</b>."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"maintenance-line\" about=\"#mwt103\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">(<span id=\"rfv-sense-notice-en-\"></span>Can we <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:Requests_for_verification/English#here\" title=\"Wiktionary:Requests for verification/English\">verify</a> this sense?)</span><link rel=\"mw:PageProp/Category\" href=\"./Category:Requests_for_verification_in_English_entries#HERE\" about=\"#mwt103\"> <span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt104\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> This <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/time\" title=\"time\">time</a>, the <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/present\" title=\"present\">present</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/situation\" title=\"situation\">situation</a>. <span class=\"maintenance-line\" about=\"#mwt105\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">(Can we add an <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:Example_sentences\" title=\"Wiktionary:Example sentences\">example</a> for this sense?)</span><link rel=\"mw:PageProp/Category\" href=\"./Category:Requests_for_example_sentences_in_English#HERE\" about=\"#mwt105\">"}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Interjection","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt108\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt109\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used semi-assertively to offer something to the listener.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"<b>Here</b>, now I'm giving it to you."}],"examples":["<b>Here</b>, now I'm giving it to you."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt111\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt112\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used for emphasis at the beginning of a sentence when expressing an opinion or want.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"<b>Here,</b> I'm tired and I want a drink."}],"examples":["<b>Here,</b> I'm tired and I want a drink."]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt114\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt115\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Used to attract someone's attention, often in a hostile way.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"<b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> You<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> Stop doing that<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>"}],"examples":["<b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> You<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> Stop doing that<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt117\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Said in response to one's name being called during a <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/roll_call#English\" title=\"roll call\">roll call</a>, indicating that one is present.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Smith ... <b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> ... Jones ... <b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> ... Walters ... ... Anyone seen Walters<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>"}],"examples":["Smith ... <b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> ... Jones ... <b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> ... Walters ... ... Anyone seen Walters<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt119\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Said to command a person or higher animal to come to the speaker.</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"\"Fido<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> <b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>\" — \"Woof<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> Woof<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>\""}],"examples":["\"Fido<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> <b>Here</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>\" — \"Woof<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> Woof<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>\""]}]}],"af":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Afrikaans","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt127\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#plural_number\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">plural</a> of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"af\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/heer#Afrikaans\" title=\"heer\">heer</a></i></span></span>"}]}],"sq":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Albanian","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt129\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#indefinite\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">indefinite</a> <span class=\"inflection-of-conjoined\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#dative_case\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">dative</a><span class=\"inflection-of-sep\">/</span><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#ablative_case\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">ablative</a></span> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#singular_number\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">singular</a> of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"sq\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/herë#Albanian\" title=\"herë\">herë</a></i></span></span>"}]}],"other":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Barapasi","definitions":[{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/name\" title=\"name